question: Sui model ū kóng Sublinear scalability, ānn-ne in-leh chí-chhî ê feature ('Pre-training', 'Multi-task') ê kî-thaⁿ sī sím-mih?
answer: TimeMixer kah PatchTST ū kóng Sublinear scalability. Iah-sī TimeMixer ē-tàng chí-chhî Multi-task learning, m̄-koh PatchTST bōe; nn̄g ê model lóng bô sú-iōng Pre-training.

question: Ū-ūi model sī-siá ū tui-chìn ia̍h-sī to-kang-tsok, m̄-koh bē-sái siang-hong lóng-ū, tsóng-kiā kā-tshing guā-tsē?
Chhōe-chhut ū *Linear*  hêng-tōng-sèng (scalability) kap *Medium*  tāng-tāng (compute) su-kiû ê model ê chú-iàu èng-iōng.
Nā-chún siat-leh gián-kiù kè-ōe iû 'Long Sequences' ê model choán-piàn kàu āu-lâi su-iàu 'Task Flexibility' ê model, hit-ê model sī tùi tē-jī kî-tuaⁿ siong-tùi siōng-chia̍h ê soán-te̍k?
列出無使用預訓練，閣有提供次線性擴展性个模型。
Soán-chhú pió-á lāi-té ê model, ū kúi-pòaⁿ hun-á su-iàu "High" ê kè-sǹg chu-gôan?
Nā-sī 'TimesNet' hō͘-lâng kiông-hòa, ē-tàng chi-chhî 'Pre-training', i ē-tàng kap hiān-chāi ê hit-ê model tī i-ê te̍k-sek (Pre-training, Multi-task, Compute, Scalability) siōng kài-kīn?
answer: Kiông-hòa ê TimesNet bē kap lēng-gōa ê tan-to̍k model sio-kīn. I nā kap 'Timer' kap 'MOMENT' lóng-ū 'Pre-training', 'Multi-task', kap 'Linear' scalable, m̄-koh i-ê 'Medium' compute koh-sī ē kap in ê 'High' compute iàu-kiû chò khu-pia̍t.

question: Ūnn-bōe kóng, model ê scalability kap i ê chú-iàu èng-iōng tùi sequence length ia̍h-sī el-tó-sèng ê tsi̍t-koân tì-tiâu, ū bô kà-lí-tiong ê kuan-liân?
answer: Ū, tsiânn-tsē lâi-khuànn, ū kuan-liân. Scalability khah-khuat 'Sublinear' ê model (TimeMixer, PatchTST) kah èng-iōng ū-kuan hām ho̍k-tsa̍p ê hoa-khui ia̍h-sī tsiânn-kuân ê sequence ('Multiscale Patterns', 'Long Sequences'). Kah-tsū, scalability 'Linear' ê model khah-tsē èng-iōng tī su-iàu el-tó-sèng ia̍h-sī teh só-tsē tsi-tsiān ê kang-khuè ('Few-shot Learning', 'Limited Supervision', 'Task Flexibility').

question: 除了 'Model' 以外，哪一欄包含最各種不同的獨特值？
Sui chit-ê model bô chi-chhî Pre-training ia̍h-sī Multi-task learning?
